en: Layer and Traits are key elements for you to randomly generate NFT collections. Both Layer Name and Trait Name are used as metadata to further decided the rarities.
zh: 图层与特征是NFT随机生成过程中的关键元素。二者的命名都将被作为元数据来决定特征的稀有度。

en: Layers are used the same as tools like Photoshop and Procreate, which allow you stack image elements on top of each other and adjust sequence.
zh: “图层”与常见设计工具如Photoshop、Procreate等中的图层概念相同，你可以将图层叠加，并调整图层顺序。

en: Traits are variants appear in the same layer. The more traits you add to one layer, the more unique each NFT from your collection would look like. The rarity of each traits can be edited
zh: “特征”是同一图层中的不同表现形态。你在某一图层中添加的特征越多，最终的NFT生成结果就会越丰富。每一个特征的稀有度都可以进行单独调整。

en: © 2022 ManeSTUDIO by Weirdo Ghost Gang, powered by ManesLAB.
zh: © 2022 ManeSTUDIO by Weirdo Ghost Gang，由ManesLAB出品。

en: ManeSTUDIO is an all-in-one solution for Web3 creators. It includes NFT generation, 1/1 NFT injection, metadata management, IPFS decentralized storage upload, smart contract custom deployment, blind box minting website building, etc., dedicated to solving all the coding parts in the workflow so that creators can simply focus on the creation itself.
zh: ManeSTUDIO是为Web3创作者打造的NFT创作一站式解决方案，工具提供包括NFT随机生成、特殊款NFT注入、元数据注入、IPFS去中心化存储上传、智能合约定制部署、盲盒发售网页建站等，为创作者解决工作流中所有涉及技术、代码的部分，使得创作者回归创作本身，是一款无需编程基础，无准入门槛的Web3创作者工具。

en: Ultimately, ManeSTUDIO is a Web3 creator tool that requires no coding knowledge and no entry barriers. NFT projects created by ManeSTUDIO will automatically generate the minting website on ManeSPACE. The smart contract conforms to the mainstream NFT secondary market protocol standards such as OpenSea, LooksRare, and will be automatically synchronized after the primary sale.
zh: 由ManeSTUDIO创建的NFT项目会在ManeSPACE自动生成一级市场盲盒发售页面，智能合约符合OpenSea，LooksRare等主流NFT二级市场协议标准，会在项目发售后进行自动同步。

en: ManeSTUDIO is free to use for project creation, it charges only a 10% service fee from the primary sale earnings.
zh: ManeSTUDIO的使用过程完全免费，仅在一级市场发售当中抽取10%作为服务费用。

key: Name it whatever you like, it can be changed at anytime
en: Name it whatever you like, it can be changed at anytime
zh: 请在此输入项目名称，可随时修改

key: Careful! Once the resolution of your collection is set, it can no longer be changed
en: Careful! Once the resolution of your collection is set, it can no longer be changed.
zh: 请注意！生成合集的尺寸比例在设定后无法再次修改。

en: We recommend you to use a safe wallet address created by hardware wallets for your projects.
zh: 我们建议创作者使用冷钱包创建的安全地址进行项目创作及发售。

en: Projects will be required to escrow funds after the start of the mint for at least 7 days to prevent rug pulls.
zh: 项目收入在发售开始后将被托管锁定7天以避免rug pull欺诈项目。

en: ManeSTUDIO charges 10% commission from the primary sale of your projects.
zh: ManeSTUDIO将从项目的一级市场发售中抽取10%服务费用。

en: Group allows creators to integrate different generation rules.
zh: 分组功能允许创作者在生成器中同时添加多种生成规则。

en: For example, your pfp project has 2 characters shaped in A and B, they both have trait 1, but trait A1 and B1 are designed with different position and scales to fit character A and B. Then you can create 2 groups A and B, then use characters and traits only in the matching groups. As long as you rename both traits “A1” and “B1” back to “1”, they will be merged in your final generation results, thus not messing with the rarity calculations. And you can change the rarity of Group A and Group B as well.
zh: 举例来说，你的项目中包含两种形态的人物A与B，他们都拥有“特征1”，但是为了对应人物A与B，特征A1与B1的位置和尺寸都会有所区别。此时，你只需创建两个分组A与B，并分别上传添加对应的特征。 只要您在分组之内把特征“A1”“B1”重新命名为“1”，那么在生成结果中“特征1”将会被合并计算、展示，不会对特征的稀有度产生干扰。同时你还可以对“分组A”“分组B”的整体稀有度进行调整设定。

en: Group can be used in many creative ways, give a try! You can always start by adding only one group.
zh: 通过分组功能可以实现多种创意玩法，尝试一下吧~你可以从新建单一的分组开始，逐渐尝试更复杂的生成规则。

en: 1/1 NFTs are special artworks that are not involved in generation process.
zh: 1/1 NFTs 是不参与生成过程的特殊款作品。

en: For example, you made some collaborations with artists and they created 10 special 1/1 artworks to be added to the 5000 collection. then here is right the place to add them. 1/1 NFTs will be separated from generation process, but will be included in the final collection.
zh: 举例来说，你邀请一些艺术家为你的5000个NFT合集创作了10件合作款作品。那么你可以在此处添加1/1合作款作品。1/1作品不参与随机生成过程，但是会出现在最终的NFT合集之中。

key: Must be capital letters in English
en: Must be capital letters in English

Repetition rate is simply calculated as “Your collection size” divided by “Max. generatable possibilities” to evaluate how unique your NFT collection would look like. The smaller this number is, the less repetition would appear in your collection.
zh: 重复率是"NFT合集数量"与"最大可生成数量“的比值，用以评估合集中NFT的独特性。这个数字越小，NFT中特征出现的重复率就越低。

en: Mediocre. It would be great to bring more variation of traits if you intent to keep the current collection size.
zh: 中等水平。如果想要保持现有的合集数量不变，那最好再添加一些更多特征。

en: Repetition rate is high. Better bring more variation of traits in last step, otherwise NFT tokens would look identical.
zh: 重复率过高。请返回上一步并添加更多特征，否则合集中的NFT将显得相似而单一。

en: You may optionally select and reserve some NFTs from the projects for your team, or use them for future business development.
zh: 你可为团队选择并预留部分NFT，或用于未来的商务拓展用途。

en: Reserved NFTs will be minted directly to your wallet, and the amount will be displayed publicly on ManeSPACE.
zh: 预留的NFT将被直接铸造至你的钱包。预留NFT的数量会在ManeSPACE进行公开展示。

en: Skip this step if you find this unnecessary.
zh: 如无此需求，请跳过此步骤。

en: Smart contract is what turns JPEGs into NFT tokens, NFTs are minted through smart contracts that assign ownership and manage the transferability of the NFT. With ManeSTUDIO, you can edit the parameters by a few clicks to fully customize an unique smart contract for your projects.
zh: 智能合约可将小图片转换为NFT tokens，NFT 是通过分配所有权和管理 NFT 可转让性的智能合约铸造而成。使用 ManeSTUDIO，只需简单编辑参数，便可以生成属于你项目独一无二的智能合约。

en: The basic information about your smart contract include contract name, token symbol, contract type and maximal token supply.
zh: 智能合约基本设置包括合约名称、代币符号、合约类型以及最大发行量。

en: Contract name is the main identifier for your smart contract and will appear anywhere your contract is mentioned. Usually the same as your project name.
zh: 合约名称是智能合约的主要标识符，将出现在提及你智能合约的任何地方。通常与你的项目名称相同。

en: Token symbol is abbreviation of your contract name, it will appear on Etherscan and somewhere like NFT marketplaces.
zh: 代币符号是智能合约代币名称的缩写，会在Etherscan与NFT二级市场等处展示。

en: Contract type refers to the standard of your contract. ERC-721 is the common standard for NFTs of single edition. ManeSTUDIO uses ERC-721A, an open source optimized version created by Azuki to reduce gas usage while minting.
zh: 合约类型是指智能合约的标准。 ERC-721 是单版 NFT 的通用标准。 ManeSTUDIO 使用 ERC-721A，一个由 Azuki 团队创建的开源优化版本，用于降低NFT铸造时的燃料使用量。

en: Maximal token supply is synchronized with the collection size you decided from previous steps, it can not be edited here.
zh: 最大代币供应量与你在之前步骤中设定的集合大小自动同步，无法在此处编辑。

en: Refund is an option we offer for the creators to demonstrate a strong commitment to the project and community. If you enable refund function, a “Refundable” tag will be added and highlighted to your project’s minting page.
zh: 退款功能是我们为创作者提供的一个选项，以显示对项目和社区的强烈承诺。如果你启用退款功能，"可退款 "标签将被添加并突出显示在你的项目的发售页面。

en: Please note that adding refundable period will lead to a longer fund escrow to your primary sale earnings, you might be able to withdraw funds partially before all refundable period ends.
zh: 请注意，增加退款期将导致你的销售收入的资金托管周期延长，在所有退款期结束前，用户将只被允许提取部分资金。

en: Allowlist is a process to get a list of wallet addresses pre-approved for minting, normally prior to the public sale phase. Users of allowlist addresses may also receive additional perks, such as lower minting price.
zh: 白名单预售是一个获得预先批准的钱包地址列表的过程，通常允许白名单地址在公开销售阶段之前提前铸造NFT。白名单用户有时也可获得额外的优势，比如相对于公售价格更低的NFT铸造价格。

en: Allowlist can be distributed through community events or gifted to other bluechip NFT holders to receive support from other communities.
zh: 白名单可通过早期社区活动分发，或自动赠送给其他蓝筹NFT持有人，以获得来自其他社区的支持。

en: Being in the allowlist does not always guarantee you to successfully mint the NFTs, as the allowlist spot might be over-allocated than the maximal NFT supply depends on the project.
zh: 进入白名单地址列表并不总是保证你能成功地铸造NFT，因为白名单可能存在比最大供应量更大的超发情况。

en: With ManeSTUDIO, you can choose to grant allowlists to selected Bluechip NFT holders, or upload a .csv file containing wallet addresses.
zh: 你可以使用ManeSTUDIO选择为特定的蓝筹NFT持有人自动发放白名单，也可以上传包含钱包地址的.csv文件。

en: Time point when allowlist addresses can start to mint. Normally 6-24hours prior to the public sale starting time.
zh: 白名单预售地址可以开始铸造NFT的时间点。通常是在公开销售阶段前6-24小时。

en: Time point when allowlist presale ends. Normally several hours before the public sale starts, or right before the public sale starts.
zh: 白名单预售地址结束铸造NFT的时间点。通常是在公开销售阶段前几小时，或在预售时间结束后直接进入公开发售阶段。

en: The maximal NFTs can be minted during allowlist presale phase. Normally smaller than total NFT supply.
zh: 白名单预售阶段可铸造的NFT数量上限。通常小于总发行量上限。

en: The maximal NFTs can be minted by each address from allowlist. Normally there is limit like 1-5 so it is more fair for allowlist addresses to get the chance to mint your NFT.
zh: 白名单预售阶段每个白名单地址可铸造的NFT数量上限。通常设置为1-5以确保更多人能够成功铸造NFT。

en: The price for each NFT during allowlist presale phase. Normally cheaper than, or equals to the public sale price.
zh: 白名单预售阶段的单个NFT售价。通常小于或等于公售价格。

en: You can choose to grant allowlists to bluechip NFT holders. Holders who have the selected NFT tokens in their wallet can mint your project during allowlist presale phase.
zh: 你可以选择向蓝筹NFT项目持有者分发白名单。钱包中持有相应NFT项目的持有人可在白名单预售阶段进行NFT铸造。

en: Upload a .csv file containing a list of wallet addresses, one address per line.
zh: 上传包含地址列表的.csv文件。每行一个地址。

en: Public sales of NFT projects operate on a first-come-first-served basis. Public sales are open to all wallet addresses. When the demand is higher the rest of the supply after allowlist presale, some NFT traders might use bots or rise up the gas to speed up the minting speed to make sure they can get one. This, sometime, causes what we call “gas war”.
zh: NFT项目的公开销售阶段以先到先得的方式进行。公开销售对所有钱包地址开放。当需求高于预售阶段结束后的剩余供应量时，一些NFT交易者可能会使用机器人或提高gas价格加快铸币速度，以确保铸造过程更快进行。有时，这会导致被称为"gas war“的情形出现。

en: Time point when all addresses can start to mint publicly. Normally starts after the allowlist presale phase ends.
zh: 所有地址可以开始公开铸造NFT的时间点。通常在白名单预售阶段结束后开始。

en: An ending time is optional. If you enable this, the sale will end at your decision, if you have unminted NFT tokens left, they will remain unminted forever. If you disable this, the sale time will last until all NFTs are minted.
zh: 公售结束时间是可选项之一。如果启用此功能，公开销售阶段将在设定时间结束，如果此时还有未被铸造的NFT代币，它们将永远保持未铸造状态。如果你禁用此功能，销售时间将持续到所有NFT售空为止。

en: Please note that once this time is set, it can no longer be edited again. Handle with care.
zh: 请注意，一旦设定公售结束时间，该时间无法再次修改。请小心处理。

en: The maximal NFTs can be minted by each address during public sale phase.
zh: 公开销售预售阶段每个钱包地址可铸造的NFT数量上限。

en: The price for each NFT during public sale phase.
zh: 公开销售预售阶段的单个NFT售价。

en: Delayed reveal is an optional function that we recommend you to enable. Before the reveal happens, all NFTs and metadata are hidden and are traded as blind box on secondary NFT marketplaces. Please add a placeholder otherwise it will appear as a broken image on marketplaces.
zh: 延迟开图是一个建议开启的可选功能。在开图之前，所有的NFT和元数据都会被隐藏，此时在NFT二级交易市场上进行的实际上为盲盒交易。请务必添加一个封面图，否则在NFT二级交易市场上会显示一张挂了的图片。

en: When it’s time, the reveal will happen automatically, and the rarities will then be calculated by 3rd party services like trait snipers.
zh: 到达预设时间后将会进行自动开图并更新元数据，之后第三方稀有度工具如rarity sniper等便会采集元数据进行稀有度计算并得出排名。

en: If delayed reveal is disabled, the NFTs are revealed at the same time when they are minted.
zh: 如果你选择禁用延迟开图这个功能，NFT将在它们被铸造的同时直接开图并完整展示所有元数据。
